  "prompt": "What kind of questions can I ask to Quora?",
  "response": "On Quora, you can ask a wide variety of questions across numerous topics. Here are some examples of the kinds of questions you might consider:\n\n1. **General Knowledge:**\n   - What is the theory of relativity?\n   - How does photosynthesis work?\n\n2. **Advice and Life Guidance:**\n   - What are some effective ways to manage stress?\n   - How can I improve my productivity?\n\n3. **Opinions and Perspectives:**\n   - What are some underrated travel destinations?\n   - Which book has had the biggest impact on you and why?\n\n4. **Tech and Gadgets:**\n   - What are the best apps for learning a new language?\n   - How does blockchain technology work?\n\n5. **Career and Education:**\n   - What skills are essential for a career in data science?\n   - How can I prepare for a job interview in the tech industry?\n\n6. **Entertainment and Hobbies:**\n   - Who are some emerging artists to watch in 2023?\n   - What are some fun hobbies to try during the summer?\n\n7. **Health and Fitness:**\n   - What are the benefits of a ketogenic diet?\n   - How can beginners start a home workout routine?\n\n8. **Science and Nature:**\n   - Why do tides occur?\n   - How does climate change affect biodiversity?\n\n9. **History and Culture:**\n   - What were the main causes of World War I?\n   - How does culture influence language development?\n\n10. **Current Events:**\n    - What are the impacts of rising interest rates globally?\n    - How is artificial intelligence changing industries today?\n\nWhen asking questions on Quora, try to be as specific as possible to attract detailed and informative responses. Additionally, checking for similar existing questions can help find answers more quickly.",
